name: 3 Seater Julian, Oatmeal Linen
filling: Foam (28-36kg/cbm)
quote: The Harris collection is great for first-time homeowners. The classic design means you'll want to keep it for years to come and the durable cotton-jute upholstery means you'll be able to.
feature_content2: Crafted in the UK with a deep seat and foam cushioning for a comfy, well supported sit. In a beautifully tactile fabric — cushions included.
feature_content: In a versatile blue shade to blend with most looks. Keep it simple, or team with the collection pieces in other colours for extra effect.
feature_content3: This collection is a press favourite, and we hope you like it just as much. Here's a recent example of who loves it and where it's featured.
feature_content4: Holds its own as a standalone addition, or you can mix and match from the collection pieces in trilby grey for extra impact.

name: Hathaway Sofa, Gray Tweed
filling: Back is polyfill mixed with duck down feathers.  Seat is 4.5" foam cushion wrapped in duck down feather.
quote: The Hathaway collection is so classically modern, it can fit in any room or house.  I love the design and quality!
feature_content2: Woven elegantly together, our hand picked weave is rich in texture and perfectly versatile for any setting.
feature_content: Classically, modern lines with low rolled arms and tufted back detailing, the Hathaway was inspired by the timeless style of English drawing rooms.  Elegant and gentle piping and solid hardwood feet details makes the Hathaway perfect for any room.
feature_content3: Crafted from kiln dried hardwoods, the frame is built for longevity and stability.  The solid hardwood feet exentuate quality and contemporary design.
feature_content4: Plump back cushions are filled with European grade polyfiber mixed with duck down feather for sink-in comfort.  Tufted seat cushions are filled with a 4.5" foam core wrapped in duck down feather.

filling: Back is polyfill mixed with duck down feathers.  Seat is 4.5" foam cushion wrapped in duck down feather.

feature_content2: Premium, American grade distressed leather, creating a one of a kind texture and quality that makes each piece unique and age beautifully over time.

feature_content3: Crafted from kiln dried hardwoods, the frame is built for longevity and stability.  The solid hardwood feet accentuate mid century modern design.
feature_content4: Plump back cushions are filled with European grade polyfiber mixed with duck down feather for sink-in comfort.  Tufted seat cushions are filled with a 4.5" foam core wrapped in duck down feather.
